    href: "https://time.com/4789145/avocado-latte-australia/",
    target: "_blank"
  }, "latte in avocado"), " bullshit by the kids on insta, which means it is the aesthetics and the process which makes it elegant, not the dish itself. The creamy sweet coffee froth looks cute floating on top of the milk and ice slurry, but only till you're done posting a story on insta and sending 178 snaps. I have no clue how people managed to get the coffee to mix with the milk as the low-density froth is extremely adamant about socializing with anything! After battling my mason jar with a spoon for 15 minutes, I threw everything in a blender, something I would've done in the first place if it wasn't for the curse of attention."), mdx("br", null), mdx("br", null), mdx("h4", null, "Self haircut"), mdx("h5", null, "3rd April, day 13"), mdx("p", null, "I woke up today at around 2AM for my usual peeing routine, looked at myself in the mirror and decided, \"aight imma give myself a haircut\". Whoever tweeted it said it right, We're going to see a lot of bad haircuts after the lockdown is over."));
